div.div: Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu Part 2

Rudeus, Eris, and Rujierd head for Asura Kingdom in search of answers. Meanwhile, Roxy sets out across the Demon Continent to find Rudeus.
(Source: Funimation, edited)

Dororo, a young orphan thief, meets Hyakkimaru, a powerful ronin. Hyakkimaru's father, a greedy feudal lord, had made a pact with 12 demons, offering his yet-unborn son's body parts in exchange for great power. Thus, Hyakkimaru - who was born without arms, legs, eyes, ears, a nose or a mouth - was abandoned in a river as a baby. Rescued and raised by Dr. Honma, who equips him with artificial limbs and teaches him sword-fighting techniques, Hyakkimaru discovers that each time he slays a demon, a piece of his body is restored. Now, he roams the war-torn countryside in search of demons.
Saenai Boku ga Kimi no Heiya de Shiteiru Koto wo Classmate dare mo Shiranai

Yuki Toyama, an introverted loner, has a secret he hasn't told anyone. It is that he and his classmate Yuzumi Takai are "sex friends." It was supposed to be a purely physical relationship. But when Marika Uehara, a popular girl in the class, began to show interest in Toyama, their attitudes began to waver.
(Source: Sneaker Bunko, translated)
